<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Blindness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Blindness,</orth> want of sight: <bibl n="shak. tgv 4.2.47" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. IV, 2, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.344" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 344</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.197" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 197</bibl>. <cit><quote>muffle your false love with some show of b.,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 3.2.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. III, 2, 8</bibl></cit>, i. e. with some blinding show.
